Description: Fender Standard Stratocaster in Arctic White. Excellent condition, neck appears unplayed, plastic covers still on pickguard and back plate. One small, minor blemish repair spot on back as seen in pics. Comes with tremolo bar, wrenches and owner cards. All the best Strat features with an alder body, 3 single-coil pickups and vintage-style tremolo. The Fender Standard Stratocaster Electric Guitar is the guitar design that changed the world. This model offers legendary Fender tone with classic styling for those on a budget. It has an alder body that's contoured to be comfortable during long sessions, whether you're standing or sitting. Its maple neck is super-comfy with a modern C shape.
